dc_description_s: This polygon data layer represents zoning for Calumet County, Wisconsin in 2017. It is a feature class within the geodatabase Calumet_Zoning_2017.gdb
uw_supplemental_s: For complete metadata documentatThis data was submitted to the UW geospatial archive in 2017. Content may be considered current as of December 31, 2016.
